s are, yes. |archive-date=2016-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160516232322/http://www.talkorigins.org/faqs/dover/day6pm.html |dead-url=no }} — [[Barbara_Forrest|Barbara Forrest]], 2005, testifying in the [[Kitzmiller_v._Dover_Area_School_District|Kitzmiller v. Dover Area School District]] trial.
